# --- VIRTUAL ENVIRONMENTS (Matches at any depth) ---
**/venv/
**/.venv/
**/env/
**/.env/
**/ENV/
**/env.bak/
**/venv.bak/

# --- PYTHON CACHE & COMPILED ---
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/

# --- SENSITIVE DATA ---
**/.env
**/.flaskenv
**/instance/

# --- PACKAGING & DISTRIBUTION ---
**/dist/
**/build/
**/*.egg-info/
**/*.egg
**/*.spec
**/bin/
**/lib/
**/lib64/

# --- DATA & DATABASE ---
**/*.sqlite3
**/nosetests.xml
**/coverage.xml
**/.coverage
**/.hypothesis/

# --- JUPYTER & NOTEBOOKS ---
**/.ipynb_checkpoints

# --- OS & IDE (Extra safety) ---
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/.vscode/
**/.idea/
# Large datasets (optional)
data/*
!data/.gitkeep

# Logs
*.log
